<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">المَلَكُ الكَرِيم:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَيْسَتْ مُصِيبَتُكَ الَّتي بِكَ بَلْ مُصِيبَتُكَ القُنُوطْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَلَطَالَمَا سَقَطَ الشُّجَاعُ وَقَامَ مِنْ بَعْدِ السُّقُوطْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{الشَّاعِرُ القَرَوِي / رَشِيد سَلِيمٌ الخُورِي}</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">ثُمَّ قَالَتِ المَلاَئِكَةُ لِبَعْضِهَا بَعْدَ يَأْسِهَا:</span> دَعُوه ٠٠<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَإِنَّ النَّفْسَ تَهْدَأُ بَعْدَ حِينٍ * إِذَا لَمْ تَلْقَ بِالجَزَعِ انْتِفَاعَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{أَمِيرُ الشُّعَرَاء / أَحْمَد شَوْقِي}</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">الشَّيَاطِينُ:</span> بَلْ قُولُواْ:<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَإِنَّ النَّفْسَ تجْزَعُ بَعْدَ حِينٍ * إِذَا لَمْ تَلْقَ بِالصَّبْرِ انْتِفَاعَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c3">{أَمِيرُ الشُّعَرَاء / أَحْمَد شَوْقِي بِتَصَرُّف}</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>